{
  "logNo": "222399338233",
  "title": "소아 성장. 우리아이 어떻게 하면 키 크게 할 수 있을까",
  "addDate": "2021. 6. 15.",
  "categoryNo": "10",
  "parentCategoryNo": "9",
  "url": "https://blog.naver.com/PostView.naver?blogId=isuhani&logNo=222399338233",
  "html_size": 215217,
  "body": "<div class=\"se-main-container\">\n                <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-4131243c-9e8e-4863-95ce-8fb657f1f16c\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-left\" >\n\n                                <div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n                                    <a href=\"#\" class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" style=\"\" onclick=\"return false;\" data-linktype=\"img\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-4131243c-9e8e-4863-95ce-8fb657f1f16c\", \"src\" : \"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/dc97c645c18fe664.jpg\", \"originalWidth\" : \"567\", \"originalHeight\" : \"567\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}'>\n                                        <img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/dc97c645c18fe664.jpg\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/dc97c645c18fe664.jpg\" data-width=\"500\" data-height=\"500\" alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" />\n                                    </a>\n                                </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-eabf343c-f420-4c54-8a7f-a4ffc8452ed4\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-left \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-ccc30c4d-d395-46f6-a7d5-86cc6753f6a9\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-61ee9153-1427-4a88-a51d-7b0a0fc22cc2\">안녕하세요. 동작구 사당동 7호선 남성역 1번출구 앞, 이수한의원 나효석원장입니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-left \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-63bcc252-e0f5-465a-a1de-f3df41dbb6eb\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-a6be660d-899b-479d-a0a4-65a9ab115608\"> </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-left \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-cd58e41d-6444-489f-bc14-a988126a2ab0\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-5665b8ab-8586-4799-b6e5-6a7abfa9b066\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-left \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-699c04d2-af75-475c-a484-795346790714\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-6173b339-d78a-4515-9acf-385b6fbdfc78\">키 크는 방법에 관심을 두는 부모님들이 많으십니다</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-left \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-864e51aa-e033-429e-bd20-1c3a7569ee9a\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-b60935bd-0d7c-4c16-9d4f-1eb6650e8e21\">특히 성장클리닉 상담을 하게 되면 첫 질문이</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-left \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-ccf7fe17-59e2-4992-a634-fcf8f0af03ab\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-76397cde-d80d-4263-ba0f-fa1710087637\"> &#x27;우리 아이는 키가 안커요 왜 안클까요?&#x27;</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-left \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-6e6f4055-4f25-40bd-8222-ff147fd58a8a\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-279462e7-a5e1-437b-8bf4-7c03b31b0e01\"> </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-left \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-ece1344e-65d1-4957-a1e1-34388ca1ae42\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-e93f3ed0-db34-4249-b8db-c67f71209f38\">이수한의원에서 우리아이들의 성장, 키 크기 방법에 대해서 알아보겠습니다 </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-left \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-d2bfe54a-65df-4a02-b670-71c189ec27ba\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-8462d75d-fb0c-442a-bc51-c8c4ff74f2db\"> </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-left \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-8ac9be3f-85ed-4bfa-bfcb-79ceb297754b\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-fa1a04c8-a2da-44c3-8c5a-2dde74d99efa\"> </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-left \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-c539e40a-e44b-4bbf-a6cf-dd29048dd6d7\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-67746833-36e9-4af0-b9f3-3a065eb94292\">우리 애 키가 안 크는 이유는 뭘까?</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-left \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-99cb449f-cb2f-42bc-98c7-bafed4e89316\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-28a684cb-ec53-443a-92d5-7faa9abc1e39\">선천적 요인은 유전요인으로 부모님의 키가 작은 경우입니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-left \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-b25d0ac5-c16a-4bd0-8764-23ebd249bf1d\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-9eeab01b-3175-485c-9f90-71a7bf738fb6\">후천적 요인은 영양, 운동, 수면, 스트레스 및 환경 등 노력하면 개선할 수 있는 요인들이죠. 외국의 연구결과를 보면 성장에 영향을 주는 요인들은 다음과 같습니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-left \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-95936c25-5992-4285-9750-111c87ce026b\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-c21be888-9509-4932-a3ed-6ba4e8019cfa\">영양 31%, 환경 26%, 유전 23%, 운동 20%</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-left \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-6375376a-3194-41cd-b851-4dedf8f32c83\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-46b68305-7648-4a34-ad2c-62d8c86a2b51\">따라서 아이가 키가 작고 성장이 느리다면 영양, 운동, 환경(수면, 스트레스)을 개선해 주어야 합니다. 그렇기 때문에 성장치료를 했을 때 조금 더 클 수 있는거죠.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-left \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-ff34af39-876a-4f0b-966c-6c33a4cc4253\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-a0c2498d-ef31-4c37-a0fd-2941a3c60754\"> </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-6a90c9f4-51be-4370-8029-c1d58c4c0bf0\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-left\" >\n\n                                <div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n                                    <a href=\"#\" class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" style=\"\" onclick=\"return false;\" data-linktype=\"img\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-6a90c9f4-51be-4370-8029-c1d58c4c0bf0\", \"src\" : \"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/6a8a35c1696d25a4.png\", \"originalWidth\" : \"519\", \"originalHeight\" : \"357\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}'>\n                                        <img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/6a8a35c1696d25a4.png\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/6a8a35c1696d25a4.png\" data-width=\"500\" data-height=\"343\" alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" />\n                                    </a>\n                                </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-055bfa49-d26d-4e09-91d9-e1e24edebda1\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-left \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-9ec81c22-d2d6-4b69-9d8c-c338e4160cec\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-3100a60c-f471-42fe-9323-8ce154aaabd4\">  </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-left \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-27c99533-986b-4c84-ab51-9c60230fafba\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-c0431358-a90c-4160-9b98-c283d84684bb\">성장치료는 언제부터 해야 하죠?</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-left \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-00d8f309-3e2b-49e9-89d5-27bf2376a138\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-38617018-d427-4f0d-877c-f7b7dc53a445\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-left \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-59c4dcdc-54e8-4d7a-87ce-a7881c350e1d\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-ec09e4ab-41ff-4ee1-a7e3-13b6d4e85a98\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-left \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-ef3b1ed0-22c7-4aac-bdc7-29fe0802a979\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-af263fbf-4be7-4e82-8085-8d4684de341b\">이수한의원에서는 </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-left \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-d690f47d-4a5a-4e97-a3a8-3d01db9334f6\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-39e8a5b7-08c7-48c8-beaa-9f4a40396db3\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-left \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-cd5d2955-4d22-4fb8-9bf1-9deca13a2e38\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-bca48d52-e58f-4ba7-a004-9c479757a353\">일반적으로 여아의 경우 만 9세 이전, 남아의 경우는 만 11세 이전에 키 성장을 평가하고 성장치료 여부를 결정해야 한다고 권합니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-left \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-3dba5756-8c96-4d1a-8d9a-46ecded37921\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-1d274eea-2a36-4102-8912-8466153936bd\">이 시기에 내 아이가 잘 크고 있는지를 체크해서 치료 시작 여부를 결정해야 뒤쳐진 키 성장을 따라잡을 수 있습니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-left \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-a359b03a-99aa-4cdc-b52f-e461eca86797\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-a47bb490-1d3c-48cd-afb5-7dee141e012e\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-left \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-c7cd1a2e-7f54-4d3b-9c93-1d69dd6b150d\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-a0431045-8ebd-49cd-a77f-966932432370\"> 그리고 소아과 검진 또는 신체 검사 등을 통해 또래보다 키가 작고 성장이 느린 것을 알게 된다면</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-left \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-7ac4c0f3-cbe1-4074-a38e-ee7745654400\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-cafacc1e-d6b6-4d3b-a829-a5b1bde929b2\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-left \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-890409d9-861e-4f89-86cd-6848ab432fcc\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-system se-weight-unset se-style-unset \" id=\"SE-eb9c8692-e634-4f9f-8a47-f48cffa19d3a\">3세 이전, 2. 사춘기 이 두 시기는 성장치료를 집중하는게 좋습니다. 두 시기가 급속성장기 이기 때문이죠. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-left \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-02b2e941-6094-4e6b-a73f-c6ce09266657\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-system se-weight-unset se-style-unset \" id=\"SE-5893f828-4fc8-4015-9735-6ddc7f1b007e\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-left \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-1357e488-7741-4e46-aced-aed24b510262\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-09e839fe-5a1a-422d-af73-e4153c6adf28\">3세전까지 1차 급성장기 입니다. 이 시기에 내 아이가 성장곡선 상 어느 위치에 있는가가 중요합니다. 3세즈음에 내 아이가 키 작은 쪽 30%에 속한다면 이후 계속 하위30%에 머물 확률이 높습니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-left \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-423c5001-b1ea-4d31-9f74-00282e30b47a\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-277c86a1-624e-4fa0-b411-3266c0f12947\">그렇기에 3세 이전에는 잘 먹고 소화 잘 시키는 게 제일 중요합니다. 그렇게 1cm 라도 더 키워둬야해요. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-left \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-b3255d35-769b-4797-b5ee-2e60a1ae79b4\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-b84d3f16-a354-4e27-86db-65303c5e2674\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-left \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-c5b5d42a-ab3c-419f-984b-cb0085294ccf\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-051fd669-5e44-48bb-b154-0a2597e7c142\">2차 급속성장기는 남자는 14세 전후, 여자는 12세 전후입니다. 사춘기(2차성징)이 끝나는 남 16세, 여 14세가 넘어가면 성장판이 거의 닫히기 때문에 성장치료의 효과를 기대하기 어렵습니다. 남자는 음모가 자라고 변성기가 오기 전에, 여자는 초경을 시작하기 전에 해야 합니다. 연령에 따라 성장치료의 방법도 달라집니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-left \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-84fc5ff0-993d-4ef9-bc63-c11eef759c65\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-c24716dc-a295-477f-a31d-adf12038812a\">  </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-imageGroup se-l-collage\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-extend\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-imageGroup se-l-collage\" id=\"SE-bd0c268c-1b5b-41f8-beb7-839964c422ee\">\n                            <div class=\"se-imageGroup-viewer\">\n                                <div class=\"se-imageGroup-container\">\n                                    \n                                    <div class=\"se-imageGroup-item se-imageGroup-col-2\">\n                                    <div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"width:50.0%;\">\n                                        <a href=\"#\" id=\"SE-d6167a98-fb4a-481d-be76-ef1474f4a9ee\" class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" onclick=\"return false;\" data-linktype=\"img\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-d6167a98-fb4a-481d-be76-ef1474f4a9ee\", \"src\" : \"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/e192af695d1c8dbb.jpg\", \"originalWidth\" : \"458\", \"originalHeight\" : \"793\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}'>\n                                            <img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/e192af695d1c8dbb.jpg\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/e192af695d1c8dbb.jpg\" data-width=\"458\" data-height=\"793\" alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" />\n                                        </a>\n                                    </div>\n                                    <div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"width:50.0%;\">\n                                        <a href=\"#\" id=\"SE-68f980b2-85c8-41e2-8b3d-5fd94d3a8ccc\" class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" onclick=\"return false;\" data-linktype=\"img\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-68f980b2-85c8-41e2-8b3d-5fd94d3a8ccc\", \"src\" : \"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/b8afac4709e41d5a.jpg\", \"originalWidth\" : \"458\", \"originalHeight\" : \"793\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}'>\n                                            <img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/b8afac4709e41d5a.jpg\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/b8afac4709e41d5a.jpg\" data-width=\"458\" data-height=\"793\" alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" />\n                                        </a>\n                                    </div>\n                                    </div>\n                                    <div class=\"se-imageGroup-item se-imageGroup-col-2\">\n                                    <div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"width:50.0%;\">\n                                        <a href=\"#\" id=\"SE-e0eb4e43-6517-470b-8100-578800d0834f\" class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" onclick=\"return false;\" data-linktype=\"img\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-e0eb4e43-6517-470b-8100-578800d0834f\", \"src\" : \"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/ba77be0a5c88cedc.png\", \"originalWidth\" : \"497\", \"originalHeight\" : \"760\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}'>\n                                            <img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/ba77be0a5c88cedc.png\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/ba77be0a5c88cedc.png\" data-width=\"497\" data-height=\"760\" alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" />\n                                        </a>\n                                    </div>\n                                    <div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"width:50.0%;\">\n                                        <a href=\"#\" id=\"SE-13a88bc7-440f-4943-a25d-29631e516867\" class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" onclick=\"return false;\" data-linktype=\"img\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-13a88bc7-440f-4943-a25d-29631e516867\", \"src\" : \"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/0ceb7d485d1891bb.png\", \"originalWidth\" : \"497\", \"originalHeight\" : \"760\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}'>\n                                            <img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/0ceb7d485d1891bb.png\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/0ceb7d485d1891bb.png\" data-width=\"497\" data-height=\"760\" alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" />\n                                        </a>\n                                    </div>\n                                    </div>\n                                </div>\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <script type=\"text/data\" class=\"__se_module_data\" data-module='{\"type\":\"v2_imageGroup\", \"id\" :\"SE-bd0c268c-1b5b-41f8-beb7-839964c422ee\", \"data\": { \"layout\" : \"collage\" }}'></script>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-c95744b2-bdd1-4824-bd3c-3fc938733aca\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-left \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-4080fdca-deb3-459a-804a-257c40842f11\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-eec89a68-6cb4-4277-bfde-32e761f57bfc\">3세 이후~사춘기 전 까지는 또래아이들이 크는 정도만 커 준다면, 지켜봐도 됩니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-left \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-1e7dc54b-17b7-424b-a374-659e9f934344\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-bb338a27-cf53-46f1-9e2a-25e1040ce5b5\">잘 크고 있더라도 잦은감기, 비염, 알레르기 질환, 수면장애 등 성장방해요인이 있다면 성장방해요인을 제거해 주는게 이 시기의 성장치료지요. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-left \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-8946b715-1bb3-478a-ad31-b6724ada4430\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-62cad9af-4d00-4736-a5a2-af46d37b5dd3\">혹여 1년에 4cm 이하로 자란다면 반드시 성장치료를 주기적으로 하면서 키 성장을 관찰해야 합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-left \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-9b0aab61-67a7-4ed2-895a-5f0218017771\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-697353c4-42cc-4302-ac54-c504b876890b\"> </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-78970fa9-facd-481c-816d-7c487305baff\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-left\" style=\"max-width:367px;\">\n\n                                <div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n                                    <a href=\"#\" class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" style=\"\" onclick=\"return false;\" data-linktype=\"img\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-78970fa9-facd-481c-816d-7c487305baff\", \"src\" : \"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/773834a4f29026f6.jpg\", \"originalWidth\" : \"367\", \"originalHeight\" : \"359\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}'>\n                                        <img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/773834a4f29026f6.jpg\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/773834a4f29026f6.jpg\" data-width=\"367\" data-height=\"359\" alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" />\n                                    </a>\n                                </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-8fc085b3-0def-4d0a-b87e-a2fa731d6ac2\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-left \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-41f68835-84f8-482d-9059-4d03ed3740dd\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-f5033a61-58e3-479e-837c-ae07fb789a7d\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-left \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-15e0b2d6-6736-4d4b-9b40-4c6335792539\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-d644c2ff-5dd7-4f75-81b7-31fc04994318\">이수한의원의 성장치료는 뼈와 근육으로 가는 한약재와 기혈을 보해주는 한약재를 합하여 키를 키워주는 것만이 아니라 몸도 튼튼하게 해줍니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-left \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-3b896a75-0350-4ab1-a1f0-2fbbda1f905d\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-cedeef7b-3537-4631-958b-2821e29c58c3\">더군다나 한약을 통한 성장치료의 진정한 장점은 성장방해요인들까지 해결해준다는데 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-left \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-ff45f005-e94a-49f0-8e16-cb4090533ca2\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-ea2ee85b-8ed2-4039-aa38-5dbbabd82d94\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-left \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-bbca2411-ebb2-4cd9-b2e3-ab375b8fb90e\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-bd743249-5b4b-4173-87ea-28180ef25af3\">애의 골반, 척추, 발 등에 구조적 문제가 있다면 체형성장추나요법으로 바로잡아주어 바른자세를 만들어주면서 키를 크게 합니다.  </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-left \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-330b9cd1-3b19-4219-8b3c-0642446a5056\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-8adb6c8e-ce51-4325-b280-8fbd59b26435\"> </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-video se-l-default\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-video se-section-align-left se-l-default\" >\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-video\" id=\"SE-d4073c62-49cd-45be-a8af-05865e7d0d8e\">\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <script type=\"text/data\" class=\"__se_module_data\" data-module='{\"type\":\"v2_video\", \"id\" :\"SE-d4073c62-49cd-45be-a8af-05865e7d0d8e\", \"data\" : { \"videoType\" : \"player\", \"vid\" : \"5B6C92546A76ECCD0F876965388A6FF9DA3E\", \"inkey\" : \"V124fac00220952d31232338657ee98c82b52407c9fed1fdf042fa0a26f6f6f4f9bcf338657ee98c82b52\", \"originalWidth\": \"1920\", \"originalHeight\": \"1080\", \"width\": \"500\", \"height\": \"281\", \"contentMode\": \"fit\", \"format\": \"normal\", \"mediaMeta\": {\"@ctype\":\"mediaMeta\",\"title\":\"이수한의원 키 성장\",\"tags\":[\"남성역성장한의원\",\"남성역소아성장\",\"남성역키크기\",\"소아성장\",\"성장치료한의원\",\"남성역성장클리닉\",\"사당동성장클리닉\",\"이수역성장클리닉\",\"남성역소아한의원\",\"사당동소아한의원\"],\"description\":\"우리 아이 키 성장이 잘 되고 있는지 체크하고 키 성장이 느리거나 또래아이들에 비해 자꾸 뒤쳐지고 있다면 남성역 이수한의원에서 상담받아보세요\"}, \"useServiceData\": \"false\"}}'></script>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-6f3fe5a3-aa20-4628-b68b-b417b7d63f33\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-left \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-5456b00d-3947-4b72-9c7b-eeffc70a9033\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-584f60f9-14c2-4737-be23-ddf9f77fae3f\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-left \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-3bcf7ee9-69ef-467d-8b72-e5fc1fed5724\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-72095206-d7c0-4092-9c19-6a1c84f1c4fd\">우리 애가 또래보다 작거나, 부모님의 키가 작다면 남성역 이수한의원에 오셔서 진료받으세요.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-left \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-39320ad8-7d76-44fa-8d24-d96a54f19f37\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-687c1062-1384-4bbe-b336-5e7ee5850110\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-d649e068-72f9-496b-aa70-2e0d08747e54\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" >\n\n                                <div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n                                    <a href=\"#\" class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" style=\"\" onclick=\"return false;\" data-linktype=\"img\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-d649e068-72f9-496b-aa70-2e0d08747e54\", \"src\" : \"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/fcdd8df44d642ece.jpg\", \"originalWidth\" : \"678\", \"originalHeight\" : \"810\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}'>\n                                        <img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/fcdd8df44d642ece.jpg\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/fcdd8df44d642ece.jpg\" data-width=\"500\" data-height=\"597\" alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" />\n                                    </a>\n                                </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-6200cd6d-707f-40ce-8790-4e356c38261e\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-4975cdbf-b210-40e4-b91c-35ef32a98fc0\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-ca2a2d15-4921-4145-8749-575088593b79\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>    </div>",
